At 04:12 PM 08/21/2002, you wrote:

>Is there any way to get the old front shift rod bushing off the shift rod 
>without taking the tranny out??The Bently manual is about as helpful as a 
>rock on this one.

Remove the cross pin/bolt from the shift link. Push the shift rod back into 
the tranny. Then you can push the long shift rod back far enough to install 
the front bushing.

